data.description:
Check out this cute  doll house in Prescott Valley.    Great area and home has a large 
 backyard. Enjoy the beautiful sunsets on your patio.   Home would make a great occupied home or a good rental.  New roof was put on in July 2022.  Enjoy this great home in a beautiful and growing Prescott Valley.  Nice bike trail behind home.    Seller will pay up to $3,000 toward buyers closing costs with accepted offer.
